title: IAA Tonight | The Return of Jimmy G AND What's Wrong with Pacman's Bengals?
description: We celebrate our 100th episode of I AM ATHLETE Tonight by talking about all of the amazing action around the NFL yesterday, including the return of Jimmy Garoppolo after Trey Lance suffered an unfortunate season-ending injury. Plus, are Pacman's Bengals are in serious trouble after losing to the Cowboys without Dak Prescott and falling 0-2 on the season.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Brandon Marshall, Adam Pacman Jones, Omar Kelly)
